The two Infecticon ships both complied with the orders and the ships 
landed where they were told to land on. Soon the tops of the ships 
sprung open and the two beings exited white and red energy auras 
surrounding their bodies.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., KSLawdogg@c... wrote:
> Various Otyebis Crew:
> 
> 
> 
> 
> 
> As numerous guards saw the two beings fly by they did not take 
notice, the 
> beings detected earlier by radar, not to mention they had announced 
they were 
> on there way.  A small satellite moved into position to send a 
transmission 
> and a few defensive emplacements were ready to pop out of different 
positions 
> in the hull of the ship and easily blow the Infecticons to kingdom 
come if 
> need be.
> 
> The transmission was sent.  
> 
> "Demonite and Diablo, please land at southwestern side of the 
Oteybis.  There 
> will be an armed garrison and an entry way for you to enter the 
Otyebis where 
> you will be alerted of ground rules.  If you do not comply you will 
be 
> imprisoned.  If you break any of the rules you will be imprisoned, 
put on 
> trial, and possibly executed.  Thank you."
> 
> (Where you land there will be about twenty different IGL guards in 
gold and 
> red uniforms of various species)
